<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="interfere-vi">interfere <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɪntə'fɪə(r)/    美 /ˌɪntər'fɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>干预；干涉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wish my mother would stop interfering and let me make my own decisions.
我希望妈妈不再干预我，让我自己作决定。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="interfere-with">interfere with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>妨碍；干扰：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Making some extra money is an option but make sure that it doesn't interfere with your studies.
赚一些外快是一个选择，但要确保它不会影响你的学习。</p><footer>外研新选必④ – 4</footer></div></div>